casebody.data:
Rene Boas, Doing Business under the Name of Rene Boas & Associates, v. Machinery Builders, Incorporated.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, with $10 costs, unless the appellant procures the record on appeal and appellant’s points to be served and filed on or before April 28, 1959, with notice of argument for the June 1959 Term of this court, said appeal to be argued or submitted when reached. Concur — Breitel, J. P., Babin, Valente, Stevens and Bergan, JJ.
